summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eighteenth Avenue Northeast from East 65th Street to East 75th Street, et al., in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 24541, creating Local Improvement District No. 2359 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
